1. Download and install python 2.7
  - install module pyserial
  - install module python-gsmmodem
2. Download source Web2py from web2py.com http://www.web2py.com/examples/static/web2py_src.zip
  - Extract web2py_src.zip to /opt/web2py
  - Copy app sms to /opt/web2py/applications/
3. Run the web2py
  - connect to http://your_hostame/admin and edit/update database email add/phone number
  - edit your zimbra hostname and zimbra user /opt/web2py/applications/sms/private/sms.py
-------------------------------------
NOW you login to zimbra user and send email to another email and cc or bcc to sms
